data.description: Lovely 2 Bed 2 Bath home on a cul-de-sac, Inground Screened Enclosed Pool. Very Possible 3 Bed room home - large family room that half of it could be 3rd bedroom with private Bath. Family Room looks out at Pool. French Doors from Dinette area to Family Room. Newer roof 2021, A/C Pool Filter, Pool redone in 2016. No Flood Zone.
